             between ten and eleven o'clock on the 29th of July; he had the necklace on then - I went to the watch-house upon information, and saw the necklace there, and also the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-98-person903">
                  MARY 
                  ANN BEVIS
               <interp inst="t18300916-98-person903" type="surname" value="ANN BEVIS"></interp>
